summary: a blurb of Harry and Bambi fighting and making up 😍 maybe sharing sweet kisses and them just being touchy 😍
question: a blurb of Harry and Bambi fighting and making up 😍 maybe sharing sweet kisses and them just being touchy 😍
answer:
Here I am feeding you guys more fluff to make up for future angst.

.

”You’re an asshole.”

“I’m a what?” Harry scoffed as he watched Y/N’s face contort with rage. Her attitude obviously irritated him, but at the same time amused him and turned him on just as much.

“An asshole,” she repeated with great emphasis. “A condescending asshole.”

It was funny how neither of them remembered what started the fight. It began with a conversation about her uni project when all of a sudden it turned into an argument. From his car to her bedroom, still the fight showed no sign of stopping. This surely wasn’t the first time they’d fought about something so insignificant, for they tend to disagree on a whole lot of things.

“It takes one to know one, right?” He said only to receive a death glare from Y/N. “Why are you so offended? You started it.”

The way she huffed and placed her hands on her hips made him smirk, he wanted nothing more than to kiss her right now.

“Fuck you,” she said underneath her breath. But as she turned away, he was quick to grab her by the arm and spin her around.

“Hey, I’m sorry,” he muttered, one hand holding her chin. “Kiss me.”

“You can’t just charm your way out of another fight, Harry.”

“Can I?”

Harry could tell the way he raised his eyebrow made her go soft though she would never admit it. So he held her face, pecking her cheeks then both corners of her lips. In a heartbeat, her frown turned into a smile. She could say whatever she wanted, but the way her body reacted to his touch already gave herself away. Soon her skirt was hiked up for him to grab her bum, and her fingers were tangled in his hair.

“Baby.” Harry breathed against her mouth, smiling into the sloppy kiss as he whispered, “did you see how fast you went from ‘fuck you’ to ‘fuck me’?”

Y/N shook with laughter and buried her face into his neck to hide her flushed cheeks. Now Harry knew she wasn’t mad anymore.

summary: Time for real talk. I was quite inactive lately, I know. But it has its reasons. My struggles with myself has come to a point...
body:
Time for real talk.

I was quite inactive lately, I know. But it has its reasons. My struggles with myself has come to a point after years that I had to see a doctor. A few months ago I was diagnosed with a panic disorder and depression. My anxiety was at peak in the last half a year, and I couldn’t bear it anymore. I know it’s a place where I can talk about it, today it’s not a shame to share something like this and it feels good. But in real life it’s hard to explain to my friends and family why I have no energy, why I don’t have a ‘real’ job, why I do things and don’t do others. The rollercoaster goes up and down and sometimes spends more time down than up. I don’t like using the word anxiety, because it’s so comon now that it lost what it means to someone with an anxiety or panic disorder. It’s not just stressing about things. It’s a constant feeling that doesn’t just go away when the situation is gone. It’s there and it eats you up from inside. If I’m honest, I don’t really write at the moment. Anything. I still love the stories I wrote, I still want to update, but now I’m unable to do that. I don’t have the ohysical and mental energy to sit down and finish a story. I really hope that some of you who are waiting patiently for a story’s next part will get it eventually and you will still be waiting until I’m better too. I am so thankful for the time you spent reading what I wrote. Thank you all!

But it’s not just bad. I’m seeing a therapist. She helps me a lot to cope with my everyday life. I have excercies I have to do. I am looking for a job that is suitable for my needs and health conditions. I’m trying my best, even when it’s just getting dressed and do one (1) thing at home. Because sometimes getting up and leaving the house is real struggle. 

If you are going through similar or the same. You are not alone. I recommend getting a good therapist. Or I’m here to talk too. 

Hopefully I’ll update very soon. I really want to, I just can’t. Thank you for reading this whole thing! 

All the love, R. 

P.S. Sidekick is officially one year old. Happy anniversary for Sidekick y/n and Harry!!

summary: What are your thoughts on the tram pics of Harry? Some think it's a setup as Mike has connections to Harry's team. Others just...
question: What are your thoughts on the tram pics of Harry? Some think it's a setup as Mike has connections to Harry's team. Others just think it was fortunate sighting. I'm not sure. Though I do find it strange a drunk Harry Styles roaming so freely, if it was just an organic meeting.
answer:
Hey love, I indeed think it’s strange as well, but this might be Harry slowly coming out. I know he he has been to lots of gay bars, but this one might be set up on purpose; they might slowly work it up to a coming out. I think Mike might be someone from the team too, someone who would do this to get Harry out there. Maybe even a friend. However I do think he was only there to take the pic. Like the picture was the PURPOSE of the gay bar trip.

❤😘thank you for the ask

body:
After party

“Harry?” Y/N asks she blinks open her eyes. She woke up to someone stumbling and a dark figure rising back up at the end of her bed. As she’s about to turn on her side lamp, she notices it’s closer to 3am on her quiet radio when suddenly he says in almost a slur of words “don’t turn on the lamp!” She can see his shadow from the streetlight in front of their window walking towards her. He has on a ski mask on top of his head which is weird she thinks considering it’s a hot late September night.

“Hi my sweet girl, I didn’t believe Mitch when he told me you were leaving for the night.”

“I told you myself I was going home, my stockings for my outfit wouldn’t stay up anymore after my garter belt broke. And I got tired of looking like a hot mess with one part riding down.” She pouted, waiting for a kiss. Harry leaned down and gave her a soft kiss as Y/N smelt a bit of liquor on his lips. “How did you get home if you’re drunk? Please tell me you left the car and didn’t drive!” “ I only had 2 beers and two shot of disaronno, but yes my love I left the car and got a ride. Didn’t want to fight with my sweet little bo peep when I got home.” “ I was dressed as little red riding hood. That’s why I had a red cape!” She sighed quietly.

Harry just nodded his head and smiled at her as he turned around and started digging into his top dresser. “What are you doing” Y/N asked fixing her white t-shirt she was wearing, “please shower before you get into bed you smell like sweat!” “Sorry sweet girl you’re not the boss tonight.” Harry said as he turned around and walked towards the bed and grabbed Y/N’s left wrist. That’s when Y/N noticed he was holding the fuzzy pink handcuffs he got as a joke on his birthday. they use them on the rare occasion.

“Harry I’m tired it’s going on 3am!” Y/N whined.

“Hush pet. We’re going to play a naughty little game hmm? Me the nasty burglar expecting the house to be empty on a Saturday night, and you the good girl, home alone sleeping so sweetly till she’s rudely woken up.” “So the truth then? Because I was being a good girl sleeping so nicely till you stomped in here!” She grumbled at him. Harry chuckled “that’s enough out of you. Now. Where’s that’s roll of duct tape from earlier?” “What do you need duct tape for” Y/N asked almost quietly. “Are you talking about the that little roll I had when I was fixing the edge of the shower curtain? Cause there’s like 4 inches left on there I swear, so i don’t know what you’re gonna do with it.” She grumbled as he stalked into the en-suite bathroom. She heard him rummage around in the bins under the sink and then silence as he walked back towards her on the bed. “Now” he started “continuing with our game, I’m the big mean old burglar, whose going to torture you into giving him the passcode to the safe in the closet”

“Why do you need into the safe mr meanie?” Y/N said becoming more awake and rubbing at Harrys thigh with her foot. “Uh huh sweetheart”. He said as he tried to find the edge of the tape, after succeeding and pulling he saw there was only a tiny bit like she said a little bit longer than his pointer finger. “Told you so” she replied with a smug grin. “ okay change of plans” Harry grunted and took the tape and slapped it over Y/N mouth. “Now, since you can’t say our safe word I’ll need you to hit your hands against the metal bar on the headboard and I’ll stop right away. Is this okay with you?” She nodded excitedly. “Alright then let’s begin”.
